{"tid":2506404,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪每個人都接受到請工人姐姐？","createTime":"2021-04-27T09:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T04:45:08.000Z","uid":21141,"like":6,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"715fcac412361d0aca54ea4fae711305de679681","tid":2506404,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:46:59.000Z","msg":"最近去朋友屋企作客<br />\n見到有兩位工人姐姐係到幫佢湊仔<br />\n我就問佢兩個陌生人係屋企你唔會唔舒服？<br />\n佢就話由細到大都有工人所以冇話舒唔舒服，一早已經習慣左，當多兩個家人咁<br />\n可能我慣左獨來獨往，請個陌生人同佢地住我真係接受唔到，最多係請鐘點幫手處理下家務，唔洗日日夜夜對住"},{"pid":"9ed9791b70f7553802a8a7e1fd70d4a3d9fef667","tid":2506404,"uid":251336,"like":47,"dislike":3,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:50:35.000Z","msg":"日頭 yes mom yes mom<br />\n夜晚 no sir no sir"},{"pid":"106760367a703c754ae6b6c4279fc347edb4afd8","tid":2506404,"uid":34293,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:50:37.000Z","msg":"有人接受到 有人接受唔到<br />\n錦鯉想點"},{"pid":"3f19ac1c430ce6c0d65e5ebcfbaf96424493e8bb","tid":2506404,"uid":188715,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"有小朋友唔用工人要四大都好得閒, 加兩公婆份工都得閒先有得諗."},{"pid":"0a7744d603f86b663e3016774f81386ecd44b36d","tid":2506404,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"106760367a703c754ae6b6c4279fc347edb4afd8","tid":2506404,"uid":34293,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:50:37.000Z","msg":"有人接受到 有人接受唔到<br />\n錦鯉想點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"想係咁意統計下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229f99a44e90858d7181adadb8af8d65fdb7faa2","tid":2506404,"uid":118120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:54:07.000Z","msg":"對我黎講屋企(home)既定義係只接受同父母，兄弟姊妹, 另一半生活，否則只會當係宿舍(dormitory)"},{"pid":"6a26fb1d3ae1d73004548d29d3a71c7c1cccd77d","tid":2506404,"uid":21141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3f19ac1c430ce6c0d65e5ebcfbaf96424493e8bb","tid":2506404,"uid":188715,"like":4,"dis